    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Chart accompanying July 11 article misstated figures on shrinkage of Arctic ice</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A chart in Science Times on July 11 about melting Arctic ice misstated the average area covered by longstanding ice. It shrank from 1,734,898 square miles in 1978-79 to 1,503,313 in 1997-98 (not 2,792,192 to 2,419,473).</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
